versas experiencias que me han marcado y que considero regalos que he recibido y regalos que tengo para ofrecer: el trabajo directo con diversas grupos de personas y comunidades (mujeres, niños, jóvenes adultos), diseñar y facilitar talleres de desarrollo personal, la práctica del coaching ontológico, desarrollar proyectos de mentoría y ser mentora, ser doula de nacimiento y de aborto, ser madre, ser amiga, ser aprendiz de la vida, dar terapias de reiki, disfrutar de acompañar los procesos de la vida retantes y alegres."}'::jsonb) on conflict (id) do update set category = excluded.category, source = excluded.source, name = excluded.name, town = excluded.town, town_slug = excluded.town_slug, region = excluded.region, regions = excluded.regions, phone = excluded.phone, email = excluded.email, website = excluded.website, socials = excluded.socials, address = excluded.address, organization = excluded.organization, description = excluded.description, summary = excluded.summary, services = excluded.services, needs = excluded.needs, stages = excluded.stages, care_settings = excluded.care_settings, source_label = excluded.source_label, source_urls = excluded.source_urls, coverage = excluded.coverage, verification = excluded.verification, details = excluded.details, updated_at = now();
